data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled among the pines, offering a serene retreat overlooking the town of Kamiah. Everything you need is conveniently on the main level. This home has had many recent upgrades to include life proof rigid core plank flooring, new kitchen cabinets with whisper closures, granite counter tops with modern back splash, New range, refrigerator, dishwasher and a built in granite dining table. The master bathroom has a safe step bathtub, handicap bars, separate shower and dual vanities. Exterior amenities include a covered full length deck, two storage sheds and RV parking. Additional storage and a two car garage are located in the basement.  There is a 2nd washer and dryer hook up in the basement if you wanted to turn the main floor laundry room back into a 4th bedroom. Don't miss the chance to make this unique remarkable home yours!
